00:07:22.960 --> 00:07:25.960 align:middle line:84%
And they're this high because
there's been so much rain.

00:07:25.960 --> 00:07:29.020 align:middle line:84%
He said, I felt
the feeling of what

00:07:29.020 --> 00:07:33.760 align:middle line:84%
