powerful story to me.

00:07:49.330 --> 00:07:52.540 align:middle line:84%
And it illustrates
a quantum principle.

00:07:52.540 --> 00:07:54.610 align:middle line:84%
Because there is
a huge difference

00:07:54.610 --> 00:08:00.220 align:middle line:84%
