00:08:02.065 --> 00:08:04.660 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to invite you
to think about that.

00:08:04.660 --> 00:08:06.820 align:middle line:84%
When I was a young
boy growing up

00:08:06.820 --> 00:08:11.510 align:middle line:84%
in a rural community in northern
Missouri, I spent a lot of time

00:08:11.510 --> 00:08:16.010 align:middle line:84%
working in a farm environment,
in a rural environment,

00:08:16.010 --> 00:08:19.640 align:middle line:84%
baling hay, mending
fences, training bird dogs,

00:08:19.640 --> 00:08:22.370 align:middle line:84%
feeding cows, all
those kinds of things.

00:08:22.370 --> 00:08:26.810 align:middle line:84%
I'd get cuts and bruises on my
hands, my legs all the time.

00:08:26.810 --> 00:08:29.310 align:middle line:84%
And I remember my mom
would always say to me--

00:08:29.310 --> 00:08:31.190 align:middle line:84%
and it was very
well-intentioned.

00:08:31.190 --> 00:08:34.190 align:middle line:84%
But she'd say, the
healing will happen slowly

00:08:34.190 --> 00:08:35.510 align:middle line:90%
over a long period of time.

00:08:35.510 --> 00:08:38.179 align:middle line:84%
She said, it will heal a little
bit today and a little bit

00:08:38.179 --> 00:08:40.770 align:middle line:84%
tomorrow, a little
bit the next day,

00:08:40.770 --> 00:08:42.830 align:middle line:90%
until pretty soon it's all gone.

00:08:42.830 --> 00:08:44.990 align:middle line:84%
And if we embrace that,
if we think that way,

00:08:44.990 --> 00:08:47.930 align:middle line:84%
if we accept that, that
is precisely the way

00:08:47.930 --> 00:08:49.070 align:middle line:90%
the healing happens.

00:08:49.070 --> 00:08:51.590 align:middle line:84%
This is a linear way of
thinking about the world.

00:08:51.590 --> 00:08:53.750 align:middle line:84%
And I'm not saying it's
right, wrong, good, or bad,

00:08:53.750 --> 00:08:55.250 align:middle line:84%
because there are
times in our lives

00:08:55.250 --> 00:08:57.300 align:middle line:84%
we definitely want
to think linear, OK?

00:08:57.300 --> 00:09:00.980 align:middle line:90%


00:09:00.980 --> 00:09:04.922 align:middle line:84%
If you're working on an assembly
line at an auto factory,

00:09:04.922 --> 00:09:06.380 align:middle line:84%
and you're putting
together the car

00:09:06.380 --> 00:09:10.190 align:middle line:84%
that I might drive later in that
year, I want you to be linear.

00:09:10.190 --> 00:09:12.980 align:middle line:84%
I want you to do everything
step by step by step,

00:09:12.980 --> 00:09:14.180 align:middle line:90%
working toward the goal.

00:09:14.180 --> 00:09:19.640 align:middle line:84%
When the scientists
designed the Apollo capsules

00:09:19.640 --> 00:09:23.180 align:middle line:84%
to take a human to the moon and
back, it was a linear process,

00:09:23.180 --> 00:09:26.060 align:middle line:84%
step by step, each one
building on the last.

00:09:26.060 --> 00:09:28.130 align:middle line:84%
So I'm making a
distinction here.

00:09:28.130 --> 00:09:32.750 align:middle line:84%
There are times when it's good
to think linear and good to act

00:09:32.750 --> 00:09:34.570 align:middle line:90%
in a linear way.

00:09:34.570 --> 00:09:37.910 align:middle line:84%
But we have just discovered,
science is telling us,

00:09:37.910 --> 00:09:41.510 align:middle line:84%
we are not bound by the
linear laws of physics

00:09:41.510 --> 00:09:44.450 align:middle line:84%
as we know them today and
that we have the ability

00:09:44.450 --> 00:09:45.470 align:middle line:90%
to be in both worlds.

00:09:45.470 --> 00:09:47.750 align:middle line:84%
And when it comes
to our healing,

00:09:47.750 --> 00:09:50.300 align:middle line:84%
there's a huge difference
between working

00:09:50.300 --> 00:09:53.810 align:middle line:84%
toward the healing and
coming from the outcome

00:09:53.810 --> 00:09:55.880 align:middle line:84%
that the healing
has already happened

00:09:55.880 --> 00:10:00.020 align:middle line:84%
or, in the case of my friend
David, coming from the outcome

00:10:00.020 --> 00:10:03.410 align:middle line:84%
that the rain has
already appeared.

00:10:03.410 --> 00:10:06.920 align:middle line:84%
Well we went into the nearest
town, Taos, New Mexico,

00:10:06.920 --> 00:10:08.850 align:middle line:90%
